posts.description: Watch 'Long Live the Pimp,' a Documentary on the Life and Legacy of Pimp C | Complex
posts.extended: Few artists were as authentic as Pimp C. Born Chad Butler, the rapper and producer earned his stripes with an unfiltered approach to music that, alongside Bun B as UGK, transformed the Port Arthur representative into an underground king.

posts.description: Streets by VICE: Austin (6th St) - YouTube
posts.extended: In this episode of Streets by Vice, we explore Austin’s rich and rather strange cultural history through the lens of one of its most iconic thoroughfares: 6th street.
